Experience Design
Variable amount per level
Awarded based on stat related to skill
Bonus for kill
Pool that can be used on any character below current highest level character


Stat Gain
Base gains each level up
+gain based on skill selected
Modified by character traits
Equipment stats added on top


Life
Gain per level 60
minimum at max 3000
Max gain per level around 30
Average gain per level around 12.5


Skill points
Skill point gain increases at higher levels
Upgrading a skill costs more points for higher levels
Roughly 150 skill points total


Equipment
Use equipment kinds unlocked and upgraded over the course of the game
